room_title: Escape room "Abduction" by Countdown Games in Lexington
room_description:
Ripped from a scene from a movie, you are about to be abducted, handcuffed and thrown into sinister steampunk lair where you discover you're about to be a test subject. Use your captor's machines and tools against him as you try to escape... or become his latest failed experiment.
You're abducted in Countdown's craziest game yet! Based around a huge two-story puzzle where you have to use gears, levers, a cannon and more to get the ball to a box which will illuminate the code to get out.
